The paper discusses transfer learning, feature transformation, and fuzzy systems, which are all related to machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper also mentions experiments on text and image datasets, indicating that it may belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the preservation of discriminant information and geometric properties of data, which suggests a possible connection to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
